com.stremebase.map

Class ObjectMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stremebase.base.StremeMap
      • com.stremebase.base.DynamicMap
        • com.stremebase.map.ObjectMap

  • public class ObjectMap
extends DynamicMap
    A map to store key-object pairs (the classic key-value store)

    The object's class must implement Serializable

    ObjectMap does not support indexing or queries by value

    Author:
    olli
